LanguageData.MSE_ArchotechClavicleModule.label: archotech clavicle module
LanguageData.MSE_ArchotechClavicleModule.description: An artifical clavicle module built by an archotech. It's harder to damage than plasteel. Even if it is harmed, it repairs itself over time. You can install it to clavicle module slot. Requires modules surgery research to install it.
